    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various horizontal structural members in a frame or paneling, as in a window sash, paneled door, or chest of drawers, or joining the vertical posts of furniture, as in the crest rail of a chair.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
